tasks.text_content:
when i login as wreckingball and go the users management screen and add tokens for a user nothing happens.
the frontend calls this url: https://localhost:54501/api/tokenmanagement/admin/adjust
with this payload: {"userId":"7036bfb8-fa39-4af5-a7e9-59907f93f760","amount":500,"reason":"fdsfds"}
and gets this response: {
    "error": "The data is NULL at ordinal 10. This method can't be called on NULL values. Check using IsDBNull before calling."
}

